# рџ“Њ Project Overview

Electricity prices are influenced by multiple market and environmental factors, including:

- Electricity demand
- Wind generation
- Solar generation
- Natural gas prices
- COв‚‚ emission prices
- Temperature

The objective of this project is to develop a machine learning model capable of predicting electricity prices and identifying the main factors affecting market behavior.

